hcc_text: 92nd Street is a pedestrian high crash corridor (top third for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile in Brooklyn)
info: At 92nd Street at Gatling Place and Verrazano Branch En 92nd Street, there was 1 severe injury in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
